name: Bruisers of the Thespin Vines
description: Hailing from the Rootmason capital city of Thespin, the Bruisers of the Thespin Vines are known for their near-fanatical devotion to becoming one with nature. Now equipped with detailed knowledge of all the birds across Kharth, and the ability to communicate with them, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
